cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC

This paper discusses natural language tasks such as information retrieval, question answering, and text summarization, which are all related to computational linguistics (cs.CL). The paper also focuses on word and sentence similarity measures, which are important in information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper compares different measures on benchmark datasets, which is a common practice in computational linguistics (cs.CC).
